author_ssm: Tania Friedel (August 2003); Jessica Shimmin (May-December 2004); Luke Martin (2008), Brent Phillips (2008) updated by Zachary Dabbs (2009)
abstract_ssm: The Frank Moore Papers document the professional career of the artist and activist, Frank Moore. Materials include notebooks, correspondence, administrative files, source materials for his work, production materials for 2 of Moore's collaborative film projects, as well as his personal library. Strengths of this collection include Moore's sketchbooks and notebooks and the meticulous documentation Moore maintained of his artistic output, including the film projects, "Beehive" and "The Miller's Wife".
